title: Successful People Think Differently About Risk, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO23
description: You ask, "What's going to happen if I take this risk?"  Andy Frisella asks, "What's going to happen if you DON'T take that risk?" According to the MFCEO, successful people think differently about risk.  They don't see it as something to be avoid, but embraced.
